Unedited Description Supplied by Transferring Agency:

HER MAJESTY QUEEN RAMBHAI BARNI OF SIAM ON ARRIVAL IN SINGAPORE WITH THE ROYAL ASHES OF HIS LATE MAJESTY KING PRAJADHIPOK OF SIAM

Description Edited by NAS:

Queen Rambhai Barni arriving in Singapore. The Queen was escorting the royal ashes of her husband, King Prajadhipok, back to Thailand from United Kingdom.

18/05/1949
